	2015 Acquisitions


	Comstock Acquisition

	.  In July 2015, Esquisto acquired oil and natural gas producing properties, undeveloped acreage and water assets from a wholly owned subsidiary of Comstock Resources, Inc. for a total purchase price of $103.0 million, net of customary post-closing adjustments.  



